<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-800">Welcome</h2>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-pink-500 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8">
    <p class="text-xl text-center text-white font-semibold">
      Welcome to our Recipe App, the ultimate culinary companion to inspire your cooking journey! Whether you're a seasoned chef or a novice in the kitchen, our app is designed to provide you with a delightful collection of featured recipes that are bound to tantalize your taste buds.
    </p>
